---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import coffeeTopiaMockup from "@/assets/images/coffeetopia-mockup.webp";
import "@/styles/global.css";
---

<section class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden">
	<div class="fixed inset-0 min-w-min h-full -z-10 overflow-hidden">
		<Image
			src={coffeeTopiaMockup}
			alt="Coffeetopia Homepage in a mockup"
			class="w-full h-full object-cover shadow-xl"
			id="MainProjectImage"
			layout="responsive"
			width={4800}
			height={2700}
			sizes="(max-width: 640px) 1280px, (max-width: 768px) 1536px, (max-width: 1024px) 2048px, (max-width: 1920px) 1920px, (max-width: 2560px) 2560px, 4800px"
			quality={100}
			format="webp"
			style="object-fit: cover; object-position: center; height: 100vh;"
			loading="eager"
		/>
		<div
			class="flex-col justify-center content-center fixed bottom-14 left-[50%] -translate-x-[50%] text-sm md:text-base text-white uppercase font-thin tracking-wider"
		>
			<span class="w-full">Scroll</span>
			<span class="flex justify-center items-center w-full"
				><svg
					width="30px"
					height="30px"
					viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					fill="none"
					xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
					><g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"></g><g
						id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						stroke-linejoin="round"></g><g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier">
						<path
							d="M7 10L12 15L17 10"
							stroke="#fff"
							stroke-width="1.5"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
					</g></svg
				></span
			>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="relative top-0 h-screen -z-20"></div>
	<section class="w-full bg-white">
		<section
			class="w-10/12 md:w-3/5 mx-auto md:mt-0 py-14 animate-fade-up animate-duration-700"
			id="about-me"
		>
			<h1 class="text-2xl font-display mt-8 mb-10">
				Coffee Topia - Amazing Coffee For Amazing People
			</h1>
			<ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-base font-textBase">
				<li>
					→ <a
						href="https://github.com/ricard0g/coffeetopia"
						class="underline font-textSemiBold text-lg"
						>GitHub Repo</a
					>
				</li>
				<li>
					→ <a
						href="https://coffeee-topia.myshopify.com/"
						class="underline font-textSemiBold text-lg"
						>Coffee Topia Live Store</a
					> - Password: <i>shorto</i>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<div class="mt-6 mb-12">
				<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
					Welcome to <b class="font-textSemiBold">Coffee Topia</b> - the
					place where coffee lovers find their <i>Carpe Diem</i>! This
					project showcases how strategic store features can boost
					sales and customer satisfaction.
				</p>

				<blockquote
					class="border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-4 italic my-8 text-base md:text-lg font-textBase text-gray-700"
				>
					"A place where coffee lovers find their Carpe Diem - with a
					focus on features that actually move the needle for store
					owners."
				</blockquote>

				<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
					Built on the fantastic and speedy Dawn Theme, I've taken
					that foundation and sprinkled some magic on top - adding
					features that drive real business results through custom
					code and thoughtful tweaks.
				</p>
			</div>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-display mt-10 mb-6">
				The Vision Behind the Store
			</h2>
			<div class="mb-10">
				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 border-[1px] border-gray-100 p-5 rounded-lg mb-8"
				>
					<p
						class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-3 text-pretty"
					>
						This project goes beyond just looking good. It's about
						creating a shopping experience that converts browsers
						into buyers and occasional customers into loyal fans.
					</p>
					<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase text-pretty">
						I focused on <b class="font-textSemiBold"
							>adding features that actually improve key business
							metrics 🎯</b
						> like conversion rates, average order value, and customer
						retention.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-display mt-10 mb-6">Standout Features</h2>
			<div class="mb-10">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
					<div
						class="border bg-gray-100 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5"
					>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
							🖼️ Multicolumn Section
						</h3>
						<ul
							class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
						>
							<li>
								Customizable columns with text and media that
								tell your brand story
							</li>
							<li>
								Show how products make customers' lives better
							</li>
							<li>
								Share the journey from bean to cup - people love
								knowing where their coffee comes from
							</li>
							<li>
								Connect brand values with what customers care
								about
							</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="mt-3 font-textSemiBold">
							Makes these numbers go up:
						</p>
						<ul
							class="list-disc mt-3 ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
						>
							<li>
								<b class="font-textSemiBold"
									>Conversion Rate 🎯:</b
								> Create emotional connections with customers
							</li>
							<li>
								<b class="font-textSemiBold"
									>Time on Site & Page Views 🕰️:</b
								> Good stories keep people clicking around
							</li>
							<li>
								<b class="font-textSemiBold"
									>Brand Loyalty & Customer Retention 🍻:</b
								> Real stories build trust
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div
						class="border bg-gray-100 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5"
					>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
							🔖 Customer Reviews Slider
						</h3>
						<ul
							class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
						>
							<li>
								Sleek review slider for showcasing real customer
								feedback
							</li>
							<li>Free alternative to pricey review apps</li>
							<li>
								Display real customer photos, names, and honest
								thoughts
							</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="mt-3 font-textSemiBold">
							Makes these numbers go up:
						</p>
						<ul
							class="list-disc mt-3 ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
						>
							<li>
								<b class="font-textSemiBold"
									>Conversion Rate 🎯:</b
								> People trust other people more than brands
							</li>
							<li>
								<b class="font-textSemiBold">Engagement 🤳🏼:</b> Visitors
								stay longer reading what others think
							</li>
							<li>
								<b class="font-textSemiBold"
									>Reduce Return Rates 📦:</b
								> When expectations match reality, fewer packages
								come back
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div
					class="border bg-gray-100 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8"
				>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
						🛒 Cart Booster - Turn Every Visit into Bigger Orders
					</h3>
					<p class="text-base font-textBase mb-3">
						A smart cart that <b class="font-textSemiBold"
							>encourages customers to spend more</b
						> by showing them how close they are to unlocking sweet discounts:
					</p>
					<ul
						class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
					>
						<li>
							Shows "Best Sellers" when the cart is empty via the
							Product Recommendation API
						</li>
						<li>
							Displays products shoppers "May Like" right in the
							cart
						</li>
						<li>
							Prices update instantly when products are added or
							removed
						</li>
						<li>
							Progress bar updates in real-time to track discount
							tiers
						</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="mt-3 font-textSemiBold">
						Makes these numbers go up:
					</p>
					<ul
						class="list-disc mt-3 ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
					>
						<li>
							<b class="font-textSemiBold"
								>Average Order Value 🧾:</b
							> "Just $10 more for free shipping? I'll grab that coffee
							mug too!"
						</li>
						<li>
							<b class="font-textSemiBold">Conversion Rate 🎯:</b>
							Clear rewards push fence-sitters to hit that checkout
							button
						</li>
						<li>
							<b class="font-textSemiBold"
								>Cart Abandonment Rate 🛫:</b
							> Fewer abandoned carts because shoppers stay focused
							on reaching the next reward level
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-display mt-10 mb-6">How I Built It</h2>
			<div class="mb-10">
				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 border-[1px] border-gray-100 p-5 rounded-lg mb-6"
				>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">🚀 Tech Stack</h3>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>Liquid</span
						>
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>HTML</span
						>
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>CSS</span
						>
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>JavaScript</span
						>
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>TypeScript</span
						>
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>Preact</span
						>
					</div>
					<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase text-pretty">
						Built with a mix of technologies chosen for performance
						and flexibility. Preact was selected as a lighter and
						faster alternative to React.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="border bg-gray-100 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
						☕ Focus on Business Results
					</h3>
					<p
						class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-3 text-pretty"
					>
						Building Coffeetopia was really fun! I learned tons
						about Shopify Theme Development and how small technical
						changes can drive big business results.
					</p>
					<div class="bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded-lg">
						<p class="text-base font-textSemiBold">Key Takeaway:</p>
						<p class="text-base font-textBase">
							The best e-commerce sites combine beautiful design
							with strategic features that improve key metrics
							like conversion rates and average order value.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-display mt-10 mb-6">What I'm Proud Of</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">
				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center"
				>
					<div class="text-3xl mb-2">☕</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-2">
						Thoughtful Features
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm font-textBase">
						Small touches that make shopping more enjoyable and
						boost sales
					</p>
				</div>

				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center"
				>
					<div class="text-3xl mb-2">💰</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-2">
						Conversion-Focused
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm font-textBase">
						Every feature designed to improve key business metrics
					</p>
				</div>

				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center"
				>
					<div class="text-3xl mb-2">🤝</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-2">Customer-Centric</h3>
					<p class="text-sm font-textBase">
						Creating a shopping experience that customers genuinely
						enjoy
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8 mt-8">
				<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase text-pretty">
					Give it a whirl! Add some coffee to your cart, create an
					account, and see how the magic happens. This project shows
					how thoughtful design and strategic features can create an
					online store that both looks great and delivers real
					business results.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</section>
</section>
